      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains rigid with zero subframe fatigue, and the drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual and a GKN variable M-differential lock. Recent comprehensive service includes a VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement using high-performance shells. The factory-correct finish retains its deep luster over an immaculate, wear-free interior. Mechanically flawless with zero parasitic draws or fluid seepage, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
